                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4" style="text-align:center">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/000000/delete-ticket.png" alt="Logo" style="width:100px;height:100px; margin-top:15px; end;vertical-align:top">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <br />
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-10">
                <p style="margin-left:90px;">Click on a button to find more interesting <b>MOVIES</b>. </p>
                <a href="/Home/PlayingNow">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" style="margin-left:200px;"><b>Playing Now</b></button>
